#API
1.For all events
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/event/

2.For particular event
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/event/<id>
ex: http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/event/1/

3.For programs of particular event
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/event/<id>/program/
ex: http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/event/1/program/

4.For particular program of particular event
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/event/<id>/program/<orderNumber>/
ex: http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/event/1/program/1/
